column5: Well the Ice is locked in again...if we keep getting these cold nights i will be out searching for Walleye before Closer on Feb 28th ...Looks like we may get one more Kick At Walleye before its done ...also the Marina is now Open for Ice fishing 12" of safe Ice ...
Are the smelt still thick in the marina? Could spell a road trip next weekend.
I am interested in this report too! I want to go somewhere for smelts on Wed..
